{"id":"extended-diagnostics/NG8106","title":"NG8106: Suffix not supported\n\n字尾不受支援","contents":"<div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/aio/content/extended-diagnostics/NG8106.md?message=docs(...)%3A%20請簡述你的修改...\" aria-label=\"提供編輯建議\" title=\"提供編輯建議\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"content\">\n\n  <h1 id=\"ng8106-suffix-not-supported字尾不受支援\">NG8106: Suffix not supported\n\n字尾不受支援<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"extended-diagnostics/NG8106#ng8106-suffix-not-supported字尾不受支援\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n\n  <div class=\"diagnostic-description\">\n    <h2 translation-result=\"on\" id=\"說明\">說明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"extended-diagnostics/NG8106#說明\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n    <h2 translation-origin=\"off\" id=\"description\">Description<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"extended-diagnostics/NG8106#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n    <p translation-result=\"on\">此診斷會檢測 <code>.px</code> 、 <code>.%</code> 和 <code>.em</code> 字尾何時與屬性繫結一起使用。這些字尾僅適用於樣式繫結。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">This diagnostic detects when the <code>.px</code>, <code>.%</code>, and <code>.em</code> suffixes are used with an attribute\nbinding. These suffixes are only available for style bindings.</p>\n\n<code-example format=\"html\" language=\"html\">\n\n&lt;div [attr.width.px]=\"5\"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\n\n</code-example>\n<h2 id=\"what-should-i-do-instead\" translation-result=\"on\">我該怎麼辦？<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"extended-diagnostics/NG8106#what-should-i-do-instead\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2><h2 translation-origin=\"off\">What should I do instead?<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"extended-diagnostics/NG8106#what-should-i-do-instead\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">與其使用只能在樣式繫結中受支援的 <code>.px</code> 、 <code>.%</code> 或 <code>.em</code> 字尾，不如將其移動到對繫結進行賦值的表示式中。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Rather than using the <code>.px</code>, <code>.%</code>, or <code>.em</code> suffixes that are only supported in style bindings,\nmove this to the value assignment of the binding.</p>\n\n<code-example format=\"html\" language=\"html\">\n  \n&lt;div [attr.width]=\"'5px'\"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\n\n</code-example>\n<h2 id=\"what-if-i-cant-avoid-this\" translation-result=\"on\">如果我無法避免這種情況怎麼辦？<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"extended-diagnostics/NG8106#what-if-i-cant-avoid-this\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2><h2 translation-origin=\"off\">What if I can't avoid this?<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"extended-diagnostics/NG8106#what-if-i-cant-avoid-this\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">可以透過編輯專案的 <code>tsconfig.json</code> 檔案來禁用此診斷：</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">This diagnostic can be disabled by editing the project's <code>tsconfig.json</code> file:</p>\n\n<code-example format=\"json\" language=\"json\">\n\n{\n  \"angularCompilerOptions\": {\n    \"extendedDiagnostics\": {\n      \"checks\": {\n        \"suffixNotSupported\": \"suppress\"\n      }\n    }\n  }\n}\n\n</code-example>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">有關更多資訊，請參閱<a href=\"extended-diagnostics#configuration\">擴充診斷配置</a>。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">See <a href=\"extended-diagnostics#configuration\">extended diagnostic configuration</a> for more info.</p>\n\n<!-- links -->\n<!-- external links -->\n<!-- end links -->\n\n  </div>\n\n</div>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - extended-diagnostics\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - extended-diagnostics#configuration\n - extended-diagnostics/NG8106#description\n - extended-diagnostics/NG8106#ng8106-suffix-not-supported字尾不受支援\n - extended-diagnostics/NG8106#what-if-i-cant-avoid-this\n - extended-diagnostics/NG8106#what-should-i-do-instead\n - extended-diagnostics/NG8106#如果我無法避免這種情況怎麼辦\n - extended-diagnostics/NG8106#我該怎麼辦\n - extended-diagnostics/NG8106#說明\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/aio/content/extended-diagnostics/NG8106.md?message=docs(...)%3A%20請簡述你的修改...\n-->"}